Malawi: Malawi is a poverty stricken African country. By growing their own potatoes, a staple Malawi food, they can feed hundreds of Malawi people.


Agriculture: The main agricultural products of Malawi include tobacco, sugarcane, cotton, tea, corn, potatoes, sorghum, cattle and goats.





